{
  "stem": "512.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But they were not-- she went back to school and met somebody else.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And she was very unhappy, so she left her husband.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I always says, oh my God, if I go back to school, it might happen to me also.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] So because we-- for us it was everything was free.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the education was given free.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Czech government has treated us very royally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How long did you stay in Czechoslovakia after you were married?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, only about three months because it was occupied by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we feared the Russians terribly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was married in December 30, 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- that he had a rabbinical license.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He married us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were a couple of friends-- there was no wedding-- no big wedding.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We couldn't afford anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everything was on rations.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even though we were children, I was a minor, I had to go to an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They should appoint a guardian for me in order I should be able to get married.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's the only way they would give license.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to an orphanage.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came, and they interviewed Morris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they finally approved of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then they asked him whether he served in the Czech army, and he didn't.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They says they you can't get married until you finish with the army.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we decide it's time to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So where did you go from there?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a Jewish organization in Israelis that they organized.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They worked with the-- with the border patrol, that they bribed them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they would let us cross the German border to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we walked.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
